{"tid":2269972,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［名人］螞蟻是政見 阿里是良機","createTime":"2020-11-03T20:13:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T23:23:22.000Z","uid":264521,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2fbef9539507b0c0cb2cabd16dd803f7255c74ff","tid":2269972,"uid":264521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T20:13:51.000Z","msg":"大家好又係我三叔燈帶炒期權時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n阿里財報好差 陣間開市急瀉恐慌性拋售就緊既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有大戶提前已經扑定put 聽日肯定順勢掟落去<br />\n至於插到邊 我答你 係260-270呀 本身都係咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有多都係許廷鏗炒上去既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定有大幅反彈 我話既<br />\n<br />\n今日同大家介紹番隻call<br />\n行權價 270/280<br />\n11月27到期<br />\n溢價推算 10蚊  <br />\n<br />\n希望今次連登仔肯放過三叔公個老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比伯母一個喘息既機會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後賺到錢 比義士一個希望<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://612fund.hk/zh/donate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F612fund.hk%2Fzh%2Fdonate&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo8txnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=625c182a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://612fund.hk/zh/donate</a>"},{"pid":"9ca0ec2a161f50b6680fb94036cec9cace16aed6","tid":2269972,"uid":264521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T23:23:22.000Z","msg":"推"}]}